00:01:27.420 --> 00:01:30.360
And I was thinking the funny thing is, in
a

00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:35.751
completely Kindle or Nook or Android tablet
world, I probably never would have read the

00:01:35.751 --> 00:01:37.330
Girl with the Dragon Tattoo.

00:01:37.330 --> 00:01:42.250
And the reason for that is
I distinctly remember where I was when these

00:01:42.250 --> 00:01:43.680
books came
on my radar.

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:47.410
