Let me back up for a
second.

00:01:52.930 --> 00:01:55.460
Some people notice the brand of shoes that
other

00:01:55.460 --> 00:01:56.460
people wear.

00:01:56.460 --> 00:02:00.280
Some people notice other people -- can't
